First, create <bldroot> and copy file config.mk into this directory. 
Next, edit config.mk and correct values SRCROOT and BLDROOT. Execute
command:
    make -f config.mk

To build all modules, use:
    make all

To build one module with name <modname>, use:
    make <modname>

Available modules are: c, cpp, java, foo, python.

Post on Habrahabr: http://habrahabr.ru/company/relex/blog/265001/
